<p><div class="left-margin" id="set-A"><h2>Mindset of automation</h2></div></p>

<p>One of the obvious benefits of IT is the automation. With knowledge to do auotmation, you can know how to:</p>

<ol>
  <li>
    <p>Save time. Some manual works can be reduced by program. You can design a desirable function by yourself, while there is no cooperation needed (for small development).</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Save money. If you ask for an IT built, you may need to pay money to skillful people. If you do all them by yourself, you need to spend time instead of money. You may save further time by taking organized courses in IT aspects.</p>
  </li>
</ol>

<p>For example, in my blog, I pick one free template and add some desirable functions by myself. I donâ€™t need to pay or negotiate to others for the final work done, and I can predict the final results by myself.</p>

