<p><div class="left-margin" id="set-C"><h2>Last Words</h2></div></p>

<p>It was a hard time to study IT major, but I get quite satisfied with the soft skills obtained. Hard skills may fade according to time, but I believe soft skills can last longer in my life.</p>
